// =============================================================================
// DASHBOARD USAGE NOTES
// =============================================================================

Note dashboard_queries {
  '''
  ## Key Dashboard Queries
  
  ### Game Summary Page
  - gold_pacers_games: Main games view with win/loss calculations
  - Filters: season, game_type, win/loss result
  - Calculations: opponent score comparison for W/L
  
  ### Boxscore Browser  
  - gold_player_boxscore: Individual game performances
  - Joins: player names, team context, shooting percentages
  
  ### Player Lookup
  - gold_player_info: Complete player profiles
  - gold_player_averages: Season statistics
  
  ### Home Page
  - Recent games from gold_pacers_games
  - Live status updates via status_codes_silver
  '''
}

Note data_sources {
  '''
  ## Data Sources
  
  ### Raw Data (Parquet Files)
  - 2024_NBA_Players.parquet
  - 2024_NBA_Schedule.parquet  
  - Boxscores/*.parquet (traditional boxscores)
  - PBP/*.parquet (play-by-play data)
  
  ### ETL Pipeline
  1. Raw → Silver: Normalization and type conversion
  2. Silver → Gold: Joins, calculations, analytics tables
  3. Gold Views: Team-specific and analytical views
  
  ### Current Data Scope
  - Season: 2024 (playoff games primarily)
  - Team Focus: Indiana Pacers (IND)
  - Game Types: Playoffs (game_type_id = 2)
  '''
}